answers.author: Derek Johnson
answers.text:
Hi Sara,
Unless you're looking for something more specific, a quick Google search for "Merchant services RFP" will turn up plenty of examples, especially if you click on "advanced search" below the search bar and set file type to "PDF". 
Here are 3 examples that you might find helpful:
RFP for City of Mt. Pleasant, Michigan: http://bit.ly/h31uxC
RFP for Greater Indianapolis Chamber of Commerce Chamber Merchant Services Program: http://bit.ly/fsaVsh
RFP for City of Oceanside, CA: http://bit.ly/fni0Ra
Let me know if this works for you, if you have any questions about how to use the "advanced search" feature or if you're looking for something else. Good luck!
Derek Johnson
